Package com.ultreon.craft.collection

Class PaletteStorage<D>

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.craft.collection.PaletteStorage<D>
Type Parameters:
D - the data type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Storage<D>, ServerDisposable
@NotThreadSafe public class PaletteStorage<D> extends Object implements ServerDisposable, Storage<D>

Palette storage is used for storing data in palettes. It's used for optimizing memory and storage usage. Generally used for advanced voxel games.

It makes use of short arrays to store index pointers to the data. While the data itself is stored without any duplicates.
